description:

Meanwhile, Hillary Clinton was approached by Project Veritas reporters seeking comment on Shirley Teter being ordered by a Federal Judge to pay Project Veritas’ legal costs from a defamation suit stemming from a 2016 investigation into Democracy Partners, and Posobiec temporarily locked out of Twitter after calling Disney ‘groomers.’
